divs: Sighting DetailsI was looking for landmarks near a location I wanted to drive to in Hacketstown,NJ. It is always good to do that when using Google Maps. I was in the street view magnification mode panning around the views with my mouse, and my view mistakenly went too high and showed the sky. The image I got is in the two attached screen shots. You can find this yourself just by going on Google Maps and going to the location I have showing in the photos. Then go to street view and move the cursor to look up. So what am I looking at here?
Summary: I found what may be a UFO on Google Maps.
trends: There have been no other sightings in at home at my computer
This sighting has never been favorited.
